node.text:
The #LifeisStrange Remastered Collection includes ‘Life is Strange Remastered’ and ‘Life is Strange: Before the Storm Remastered’.

Both award-winning games have been remastered with updated visuals across characters & environments.

node.title: Life is Strange Remastered Collection - E3 2021 Official Trailer

node.text: The Awesome Adventures of Captain Spirit is out now for FREE on Xbox One, PlayStation 4 and PC (Steam). The Awesome Adventures of Captain Spirit contains mature language and themes.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Life is Strange on July 23, 2021. May be an illustration of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
Looks like Alex is cycling through her #LifeisStrange soundtrack collection! Which is the last one you listened to?

Thanks to Tobyja for this awesome piece of Life is Strange #TrueColors fan art!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Life is Strange on July 22, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text.
Photo by Life is Strange on July 21, 2021. May be an anime-style image of 1 person.

node.text:
We are delighted to share our next piece of commissioned art for #LifeisStrange #TrueColors - a striking image of Alex Chen by the amazing @Kloodwig!⁣
⁣
Life is Strange: True Colors is out September 10 and is available to Pre-Order Now through the link in our bio!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Life is Strange on July 19, 2021. May be an illustration of 2 people.

node.text: Alex... meet Steph! Who else is in love with this #LifeisStrange #TrueColors fan art by @ArainMorn? 😍

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Life is Strange on July 15, 2021. May be an anime-style image of 2 people and text.

node.text:
Following on from #LifeisStrange Coming Home, the first issue of the heart-wrenching conclusion of Max and Chloe's comics journey in 'Settling Dust' will include a fantastic range of covers.⁣
⁣
Pre-order your favorite from Titan Comics!⁣
⁣
Have some catch up reading to do? comiXology are running a sale on all Life is Strange comics until July 19. All links in our bio!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Life is Strange on July 13, 2021. May be an illustration of 1 person.

node.text:
Alex Chen, on the move! Check out this lovely piece of #LifeisStrange #TrueColors fan art by Deviantart user Duca Baumgarten!⁣
⁣
If you could go anywhere right now, where would you go?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Life is Strange on July 10, 2021. May be an anime-style image of one or more people and text.

node.text: Press X to hug! Here's a super cute piece of #LifeisStrange2 fan art of Sean and Finn by @w4ylin!
